General.Name: Douugh Ltd
General.Description: Douugh Limited, a financial technology company, provides smart mobile banking applications. Its Douugh mobile application offers personal checking account, a Mastercard debit card, account aggregation, and payment services. The company was founded in 2016 and is based in Haymarket, Australia.

1.Name: Mr. Mark David Taylor
1.Title: Co-Founder and Chief Product & Marketing Officer
